                "description_en": "Overture, Almere (approx. 100 m2) €1600 excl. G/W/E<br />\nThis nice and spacious apartment is located on the fourth floor of a well-maintained apartment complex. It is located on a quiet street and offers a wide view of the adjacent water and the neighborhood behind it. The apartment is accessible via the stairs or elevator. <br />\n<br />\nThe entrance/hall provides access to all rooms. The living room provides access to the spacious balcony. The balcony is located on the south-east. The living room also provides access to the kitchen. The kitchen is fully equipped, such as a 4-burner induction hob, extractor fan, dishwasher, combi oven and a fridge-freezer combination. The large bedroom offers enough space for a double bed and a spacious wardrobe. The second bedroom is also spacious in size and can also be furnished with a double bed and wardrobe. The bathroom has a walk-in shower, sink and bathtub. The toilet is located separately in the hall. <br />\n<br />\nThe house is located in the highly sought-after Muziekwijk. The location of the house is ideal, close to all amenities such as shops, station, public transport, sports clubs and (international) schools. The roads to Amsterdam can be reached within a few minutes by car.",
