                "description_en": "REGISTRATION FOR THIS PROPERTY IS CLOSED. WE WILL NO LONGER ACCEPT NEW VIEWING REGISTRATIONS.<br />\n<br />\nMauritsstraat, Haarlem/Centre (approx. 70m2) €1400,- Excl. G/W/E<br />\nThis furnished ground floor apartment is located in a fantastic location. The house can be reached through the joint entrance. The hall gives access to the spacious living room with a beautiful wooden herringbone floor and high windows. The open kitchen has a beautiful cooking island and is equipped with all necessities such as an induction hob, dishwasher, combi oven, fridge and freezer. There is also a separate toilet in the hall. The spacious bedroom is located at the rear of the building. Through the bedroom there is access to the modern bathroom with walk-in shower and double sink. Separate room with washing machine and dryer, which provides access to the communal bicycle shed through the back door.<br />\n<br />\nParticularities:<br />\n- Available for a minimum of 12 months (Type A contract)<br />\n- NO pets allowed<br />\n- Maximum 1 person<br />\n- Available immediately<br />\n- On top of the rent there is a fixed amount of € 250 per month for G/W/E and € 10 service costs",
