                "description_en": "Schoterstraat, Haarlem / Frans Halsbuurt, Center (approx. 82 m2) €1950,- Excl. G/W/E<br />\nAt a fantastic and popular location in Haarlem, we offer this fully renovated and characteristic upstairs apartment. This attractive upstairs apartment with private entrance is situated on the 1st and 2nd floor and has a neat laminate floor in its entirety. The living room is wonderfully light and has a cozy bay window and upper windows that are characterized by characteristic stained glass. The large open kitchen with bar is equipped with modern built-in appliances such as a refrigerator, freezer, dishwasher and gas stove. Next to the stairs to the second floor is a spacious indoor storage space. On the second floor there are two spacious bedrooms, both with new wardrobes. From the bedroom at the rear there is access to the sunny roof terrace of approximately 14 m2. New bathroom with spacious walk-in shower, double sink, toilet and connection for washing machine and dryer. In short: the perfect home for tenants who would like to live in a central location, but in a quiet street that is only a 3-minute walk from the central station. The center of Haarlem and the shopping street \"de Cronjé\" are also within walking distance. Street parking is possible with a parking permit. Definitely worth a visit!<br />\n<br />\nParticularities<br />\n- Available for a minimum of 12 months<br />\n- No pets allowed<br />\n- Utilities and television/internet in your own name and account",
