                "description_en": "Florapark, Haarlem/ Centre  (approx. 70m2) € 1750,- Excl. G/W/E<br />\nOn the first floor of this beautiful historic building, this bright and fully furnished apartment is available. The whole property was recently renovated and furnished with good sense of style. Each apartment is luxuriously finished and furnished. The apartment is with a bedroom, spacious bathroom with shower, sink and a washing machine and dryer. The open kitchen is equipped with fridge / freezer, gas hob with extractor hood, combination oven and a dishwasher. Behind the villa are private parking spots available at a rate of € 75 per month. Living in this building is really an experience. Excellent location in relation to the cozy Haarlem city center, roads to Amsterdam and Schiphol and public transport. <br />\nIdeal home for expats!<br />\n<br />\nParticularities:<br />\n- Suitable for a couple or 1 person<br />\n- No pets allowed<br />\n- Available for a minimum of 12 months, per February 1st<br />\n- On top of the rental price, there is an advance g/w/e of € 250.00 and service costs of € 60.00",
