                "description_en": "Pa Verkuyllaan, Badhoevedorp (approx. 40m2) € 950, - Excl. G/W/E <br />\nBeautifully furnished studio, located in a convenient location near the center of Badhoevedorp. Shared entrance with hall, stairs to the second floor with access to the studio. The room is very bright by the double dormer. Cozy and furnished with a seating area and a double bed. The kitchen provides among other things an electric hob and fridge/freezer. On either side of the studio is plenty of storage space. The private bathroom has a shower and a toilet. The studio is located on a nice street with lots of greenery. Bus stop in front of the door with direct connections to Amsterdam (15 min.), Haarlem (20 min.), and Schiphol (20 min.). Easy access to the highways and free parking around the corner. Sports facilities and the various roads are also a short distance away. The various buses have a stop a short distance away and the connection to the new A9 has also become more favorable. There is ample parking space in front of the door.",
