                "description_en": "Hermitage, Zaandam (approx. 122m2) € 2100,- Excl. G/W/E and service costs<br />\nBeautiful apartment with large windows and fantastic views located on the 11th floor in the center of Zaandam. The entrance gives access to the corridor from which all areas are accessible. The bright and open living room with large windows offers a view over Zaandam and even as far as Amsterdam. The adjacent balcony of approximately 6 m2 is located on the south. The open kitchen is equipped with a dishwasher, induction hob, microwave oven combination and plenty of storage space. The master bedroom is spacious and has an adjoining walk-in closet. The large windows give a view to the north. The adjacent bedroom is also spacious and faces west and north. The third bedroom is equipped with a large wardrobe and storage cupboard. Here it is possible to create a workplace. The bathroom overlooks the \"Zaanse wooden houses\" and is equipped with a separate bath, walk-in shower, sink and towel radiator. There is a communal garden on the 2nd floor.<br />\nUnder the building is a large underground parking space where it is possible to take out a subscription.<br />\nSupermarkets and shops can be reached under the building and Zaandam station and other public transport are also within walking distance.",
