                "description_en": "Uranusstraat, Haarlem-Noord (approx. 110m2) € 2750,- Excl. G/W/E<br />\n<br />\nBeautiful, furnished family home in a great location in Haarlem-Noord. The house is characterized by the very tasteful decor, combined with the authentic details that this 1930s home is rich in. Located in a quiet residential area in the Planetenbuurt, within walking distance of the nearby shopping street and within cycling distance of the lively center of Haarlem. Various roads can be reached within a few minutes. A perfect, furnished family home. Entrance accessible through the spacious front garden. Vestibule with beautiful granite floor and space for hanging coats. Hall with stairs to the top and authentic tiled wall. Separate toilet in the hall. Beautiful living room with bay window and original stained glass windows and lovely open kitchen. Patio doors to the garden. The modern open kitchen is equipped with all modern appliances such as a dishwasher, induction hob and has plenty of storage space.<br />\n<br />\nThe spacious backyard can also be reached through the kitchen. The beautifully landscaped and well-maintained backyard is located on the and has a storage shed and back.<br />\n<br />\nFirst floor with landing, three bedrooms, and bathroom.<br />\nTwo bedrooms are located at the front of the house. The most spacious bedroom at the rear of the house has a wardrobe, double bed and patio doors to the balcony overlooking the garden. Next to this bedroom is the luxurious bathroom with rain shower, bath, toilet and washbasin.<br />\n<br />\nOn the second floor there are two more spacious rooms, the room at the front of which is furnished as an office. Laundry room with washing machine and dryer. This beautiful and attractive house is very suitable for a family, both the house itself and the location. Definitely worth a visit!<br />\n<br />\nParticularities:<br />\n- Available for a minimum of 12 and a maximum of 12 months.<br />\n- 2 months deposit<br />\n- Available from 10-01-2023<br />\n<br />\n",
